This was a simple and delicious dish. I am not a cheese connoisseur so I used feta instead which was delicious. For those without an ovenproof skillet - I saw this on a cooking show once and it works for things that will only be under the broiler briefly - wrap the plastic or wooden handle in a couple layers of aluminum foil and your handle will not be damaged by the heat. I reuse the same piece of foil so I'm not wasting foil every time I use this trick - one of these days I'll just buy the darned ovenproof pan!

